When a Power Word, Kill spell is uttered, one creature within the spell range is slain. The power word slays a creature with up to 59 hit points. Even if the creature's maximum hit points are higher than 59, the current hit points are used for this determination. There is no saving throw. This spell has no effect if the target has more than 59 hit points.~

