CONJURE CLAN SPIRIT: Members of the Avenger sect practice a ritual that brings them into a state of shared consciousness. As their grasp on each others' internal energy increases, clan members gain an ability to call forth an ancestral spirit. The spectre will possess abilities and powers of the source, but the strength depends directly on the summoner's experience.

